annotationA: CG9865, isoform A; Transferase activity, transferring hexosyl groups. It is involved in the biological process described with: GPI anchor biosynthetic process
annotationB: Phosphatidylinositol-glycan biosynthesis class W protein; Probable acetyltransferase, which acetylates the inositol ring of phosphatidylinositol during biosynthesis of GPI- anchor
